hcc_text: Cedar Avenue is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in the Bronx)
info: At Cedar Avenue at Major Deegan Exwy Nb En West 179th Street, West 179th Street and Major Deegan Exwy Nb Exit 8, there were 22 injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
